OL,3,CScotland scraps peak-time train fares
OL,4,Cin 'historic' shake-up for rail
OL,5,Cpassengers
OL,7,FPeak-time train fares in Scotland have
OL,8,Fbeen scrapped from Monday in what has
OL,9,Fbeen described as a "historic moment".
OL,11,FThe Scottish government announced the
OL,12,Fchange earlier this year after
OL,13,Fpreviously rejecting it, saying a year-
OL,14,Flong trial had not been widely used.
OL,16,FThe decision means commuters will pay
OL,17,Fless to travel in the mornings or
OL,18,Fevenings, with the price of a return
OL,19,Fticket between Glasgow and Edinburgh
OL,20,Ffalling from #32.60 at peak times to
OL,21,F#16.80.
