OL,7,FFirst Minister John Swinney said the
OL,8,Fchange will help those struggling with
OL,9,Fthe soaring cost of living.
OL,11,F"The SNP government is relentlessly
OL,12,Ffocused on delivering on the
OL,13,Fpriorities of the people of Scotland,
OL,14,Fand this week we are hitting the
OL,15,Fground running by delivering cheaper
OL,16,Ftrain fares," Swinney said.
