OL,7,F"Abolishing peak fares is an historic
OL,8,Fmoment for Scotland's railway,
OL,9,Foffering the chance for a step-change
OL,10,Fin how people travel which can deliver
OL,11,Fsignificant progress in our fight
OL,12,Fagainst climate change.
OL,14,F"This is also a crucial way for us to
OL,15,Fprovide support for people during the
OL,16,Fcost-of-living crisis and to put money
OL,17,Fback into people's pockets at a time
OL,18,Fwhen many are really struggling."
