OL,7,FHe added that the UK government has
OL,8,F"nothing to offer," while his
OL,9,Fministers are "taking determined
OL,10,Faction to support people during tough
OL,11,Ftimes".
OL,13,FScotRail managing director Joanne
OL,14,FMaguire said that rail travel in
OL,15,FScotland will now be "simpler, more
OL,16,Fflexible and provide better value for
OL,17,Fmoney".
