OL,7,FThe train drivers' union Aslef
OL,8,Fwelcomed the end of peak fares but
OL,9,Fsaid ticket prices still need to be
OL,10,Fcut further.
OL,12,FAslef Scottish organiser Kevin Lindsay
OL,13,Fsaid: "The permanent scrapping of peak
OL,14,Ffares is a victory for rail
OL,15,Fpassengers, the environment, our wider
OL,16,Feconomy and the future wellbeing of
OL,17,FScotland's rail industry.
