OL,5,Cpassengers
OL,7,F"We are pleased that the government
OL,8,Ffinally saw sense and resolved to
OL,9,Fsupport the scrapping of peak fares,
OL,10,Fending the de-facto extra tax on
OL,11,Fworkers and making rail more
OL,12,Faffordable for them and other
OL,13,Fpassengers when travelling during so-
OL,14,Fcalled peak times."
OL,16,FThe Scottish Greens, who pushed for
OL,17,Fthe move while in government, said the
OL,18,Fchange is a "big step in the right
OL,19,Fdirection".
